// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2566 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 023a4c67-39df-5dfd-8405-db347e819051

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*photon os:4.0*")
